description:
1 Import Videos/DVD into the software
Click "Add Files" button to load videos, or click "Load DVD" in the primary window and select items in the dialog that appears to import physical DVD or DVD files (VIDEO_TS) to the program. You'll see the imported files listed in window, shown at the left and click to enlarge.

2 Select an output format
Select your desired output format on the right of the primary window - click the format icon or click the drop-down menu. You can easily select a preset for your mobile devices, which is defaulted the format as well as the optimized resolution, frame rate, etc. To convert 2D video to 3D, go to 3D section in Format category and choose any 3D output format offered according to your needs.

3 Start to convert DVD or video file
After everything is set up, simply click the Convert or Burn button. All tasks will be started or in queue. You can pause any task or cancel conversion as you want.

How to Uninstall Video Converter Ultimate
Go to Start > All Programs > iSkysoft > Video Converter Ultimate. You'll see the "Uninstall Video Converter Ultimate" item, click it and follow the on-screen instructions to remove Video Converter Ultimate from your system.
